metadata.name: CatGuy #6540
metadata.description:
Ownn! Catguy! is a collection of unique non-fungible tokens (NFTs) that reside on the Ethereum blockchain. Each CatGuy is hand-crafted during a careful generative method, leading to unique characters for everyone.

CatGuy is the main character from our upcoming animated project.
Help CatGuy escape from his crypto-prison and merge with our carbon-based world.
